reviewText: wonderful...wish i could find more...but dad enjoyed it..still watching vhs tapes ..lol..o well order was fine and came as expexted on time!!!

I am old enough to have watched the first Show of Shows and seen the cast change and grow over the years, especially with the addition of Imogene Coca.  With the death of Sid Caesar, I bought this tape to transfer to DVD for my collection of nostalgia.
Really enjoyable and took us back to our younger days.  Great fun for the whole family.  Video in excellent condition, too.  Thanks for good service and quality.
